org.conqat.engine.sourcecode.coverage

Class ProbeCoverageInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.engine.sourcecode.coverage.ProbeCoverageInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ProbeCoverageInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Holds coverage information for a file represented as "probes". See CoverageProbeBase for a description of probes. We use this object both to represent covered and coverable information. The flag uploaded differs between the two cases.
    See Also:
